\v 11 Being enriched in every thing to all bountifulness, which causeth
through us thanksgiving to God. 
\v 12 For the administration of this service not only supplieth the want of
the saints, but is abundant also by many thanksgivings unto God; 
\v 13 Whiles by the experiment of this ministration they glorify God for your
